I"¢<p>At 18th level, you can take retribution on those who dare to strike an agent of his faith. Whenever an enemy makes a successful melee attack against you or an adjacent ally devoted to the same faith, you can use your reaction to strike the enemy. You have advantage on this attack. If the attack made by the enemy was a critical hit, you have advantage on any damage rolls resulting from your reaction as well.</p>
